tion which could give rise to formal action being taken by them to ensure compliance.</p> <p>I have also included a Health and Safety Compliance Review which comprises of a detailed overview of your current health and safety rating using a traffic light system.</p> <p>Should you require any further support or wish to discuss how we can further assist you in achieving health and safety compliance. Please do not hesitate to contact me or ring our 24 hour Advice Service on 0844 892 2772 option 2.</p> <p>Yours sincerely,</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>Diana Howlett<br /><br /> Email address : diana.howlett@peninsula-uk.com</p>";

        [Test]
        public void given_base64_encoded_string_is_used_for_letterhead_then_its_replaced_with_new_letterhead_html()
        {
            var result = ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.UpdateLetterHeaderHtml(base64LetterheadCoveringLetter);
            Assert.IsTrue(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.NewLetterheadHtml));
            Assert.IsFalse(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.Base64LetterheadHTML));
            Assert.IsFalse(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.PeninsulaLogoLetterheadHTML));
        }

        [Test]
        public void given_link_to_peninsula_logo_is_used_for_letterhead_then_its_replaced_with_new_letterhead_html()
        {
            var result = ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.UpdateLetterHeaderHtml(peninsulaLogoLetterheadCoveringLetter);
            Assert.IsTrue(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.NewLetterheadHtml));
            Assert.IsFalse(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.PeninsulaLogoLetterheadHTML));
            Assert.IsFalse(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.Base64LetterheadHTML));
        }

        [Test]
        public void given_link_to_peninsula_letterhead_image_is_used_for_letterhead_then_nothing_changes()
        {
            var result = ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.UpdateLetterHeaderHtml(peninsulaLetterheadAsImageLetterheadCoveringLetter);
            Assert.AreEqual(peninsulaLetterheadAsImageLetterheadCoveringLetter, peninsulaLetterheadAsImageLetterheadCoveringLetter);
            Assert.IsFalse(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.PeninsulaLogoLetterheadHTML));
            Assert.IsFalse(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.Base64LetterheadHTML));

        }

        [Test]
        public void given_no_letterhead_html_is_present_then_html_letterhead_is_added()
        {
            var result = ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.UpdateLetterHeaderHtml(noLetterheadCoveringLetter);
            Assert.IsTrue(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.NewLetterheadHtml));

        }

        [Test]
        public void given_letterhead_contains_too_many_line_breaks_for_visit_address_then_these_are_removed()
        {
            var letterHead = "<p class=\"pbs-letterhead\"><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /><br /></p>";
            var result = ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.UpdateLetterHeaderHtml(letterHead);

            Assert.IsTrue(result.Contains(ExecutiveSummaryLetterHeadFixer.NewLetterheadHtml));

            Assert.IsFalse(result.Contains(letterHead));
        }

